\f0\b0 \cf0 Some commands (e.g. \'d2man\'d3) automatically invoke a text pager for their output. These commands get the name of the pager to use from the environment variable PAGER. To use AquaLess with these programs, set the variable to \'d2aless\'d3, like this:\
