\f0\b0 \cf0 AquaLess supports the special codes used by \'d2man\'d3 to encode bold and underlined words in plain text. This processing can be disabled using the popup menu at the bottom of each text window. The popup also allows you to select a \'d2Hex dump\'d3\'camode, which is more suitable for binary (i.e. non-text) files.\
